quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,166,"Ko he…ďi on kon √Īande dente …óen …ói…óe fottunoo, ko e DuŇčayee(sakkitoore) Alla, e fii no Alla Anndira goŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  3,167,"e no O Anndira …ďen naafiqii…ďe, …ďe wi'anaa: "ngaree ka…ďe…óon fii laawol Alla ngol maa du√Īon". ∆Āe wi'i: "Si me…óen ganndunoo hare men jokkay on". Kam…ďe nden √Īande heen, ko keeferaaku ngun …ďurnoo …ďa…ótaade e dii goŇč…óinal ngal : hi…ďe wowlira kunndu…óe ma…ď…ďe ko alaa e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe. Ko Alla ∆Āuri Anndude ko …ďe soomi."
  3,168,"∆Āeen wi'an…ďe musi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe, …ďe njoo…óii: "Si tawno …ďe …óoftino men, …ďe mbaretanooke". Makku: "Pottinee maayde nden e pittaali mo'on si on laatike gooŇč…óu…ďe!"."
  3,169,"Wata a sikku …ďen waraa…ďe fii laawol Alla ngol ko maayu…ďe, ko woni: ko wuuru…ďe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe hi…ďe arsikinee,"
  3,170,"hi…ďe mbeltori ko Alla Okki …ďe kon e ∆Āural Makko, hi…ďe mbeltina …ďen [si…ó…ďe] ma…ď…ďe …ďe …ďe hawraani e mu'un …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, wonnde kulol alanaa …ďe, wanaa kam…ďe woni ko sunoytoo."
  3,171,"Hi…ďe mbeltora( weltoro) dokke immo rde ka Alla e …ďural. E wonnde pellet, Alla yeebataako njo…ďdi goŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  3,172,"∆Āen nootii…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo on …ďaawo nde barmeere nden he…ďi …ďe. Hino woodani …ďen mo∆ī∆īin…ďe e ma…ď…ďe …ďe kulii Alla, njo…ďdi mawndi."
  3,173,"∆Āen …ďe yim…ďe …ďen wi'annoo: "Pellet yim…ďe …ďen moo…ďanike on, kulee…ďe". ∆äum …ďeydi …ďe goŇč…óinal, …ďe wi': "Alla yonii men, O mo∆ī∆īii yonndinoraa…óo"."